'''Estadio Municipal Doctor Mario Sobrero''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Rocha, Uruguay|Rocha]], [[Uruguay]]. It is currently used primarily for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches. The stadium holds 8,000 people and was built in 1955.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/south_america/countries/uruguay.shtml |title=Stadiums in Uruguay|publisher=Worldstadiums.com|accessdate=12 September 2011}}</ref> It is the home stadium of [[Rocha F.C.]]
