{{Infobox sport governing body |name = Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme |abbrev = LMA |logo = Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme Logo.png |logosize = 233px |sport = [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]] |category = |image = |caption = |jurisdiction = |founded = {{Start date|2008}} |aff = [[Fédération française d'athlétisme]] |affdate = |region = |regionyear = |headquarters = |location = [[Fort-de-France]] |president = [[Claude CHERY]] |chairman = |chairperson = |chair = |chiefexec = |vicepresident = [[Véronique MARIE-JOSEPH]] |secretary = [[Sandra JENASTE]] |coach = |womenscoach = |key staff = |operating income = |sponsor = |year closed = |replaced = Ligue Régionale d'Athlétisme de Martinique |prevfounded = |url = liguemque.athle.com |countryflag = |countryflag2 = |countryflag3 = |more = [[File:Flag of France.svg|40px]] / [[File:Drapeau aux serpents de la Martinique.svg|40px]] }}
The '''Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme''' ('''LMA''') is the governing body for the sport of athletics in [[Martinique]]. The current president is [[Max Morinière]].<ref name=lma_5> {{ Citation | last = | first = | date = | title = COMITE DIRECTEUR DE LA LMA EN DATE DU 04 DECEMBRE 2012 | url = http://liguemque.athle.com/upload/ssites/001148/la_ligue/comite_directeur_de_la_lma_au_04_dec_2012.pdf | publisher = Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme | page = | language = French | accessdate = January 9, 2013 }} </ref> He was elected for the first time in November 2010,<ref name=lma_1> {{ Citation | last = | first = | date = | title = NOUVEAU COMITE DIRECTEUR DE LA LMA EN DATE DU 23 NOVEMBRE 2010 | url = http://acsalon.athle.com/upload/ssites/001148/la_ligue/comite_directeur_de_la_lma_en_date_du_23_novembre_2010.pdf | publisher = Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme | page = | language = French | accessdate = October 18, 2012 }} </ref> and re-elected in October 2012.<ref name=lma_4> {{ Citation | last = DELIN | first = Lydia | date = October 10, 2012 | title = ASSEMBLEE ORDINAIRE ELECTIVE DE LA LMA - Max MORINIERE REELU PRESIDENT | url = http://liguemque.athle.com/asp.net/espaces.news/news.aspx?id=113502 | publisher = Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme | page = | language = French | accessdate = January 9, 2013 }} </ref>
As LMA is part of the [[Fédération française d'athlétisme]], athletes from Martinique normally participate internationally for France, for example, in the [[European Athletics Championships]] as organized by the [[European Athletic Association|EAA]]. On the other hand, Martinique as a French [[overseas department]] is part of the [[Caribbean]]. As an observer member of [[Central American and Caribbean Athletic Confederation|CACAC]], Martinique is invited to participate at the championships, and also at the [[CARIFTA Games]].
== History == LMA was founded on November 29, 2008, replacing the ''Ligue Régionale d'Athlétisme de Martinique''.<ref name=antilles_sport>{{ Citation |last = |first = |date = December 1, 2008 |title = Composition de la Ligue de Martinique d'Athlétisme - La ligue fait peau neuve |url = http://antilles-sport.com/actu/disciplines/Athletisme/Martinique/athl-mqe37.asp |publisher = Antilles-Sport.com |page = |language = French |accessdate = October 18, 2012 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120516142309/http://www.antilles-sport.com/actu/disciplines/Athletisme/Martinique/athl-mqe37.asp# |archive-date = 2012-05-16 |dead-url = yes |df = }}</ref>
== Affiliations == *[[Fédération française d'athlétisme]] (FAA) LMA is an observer member federation for [[Martinique]] in the *[[Central American and Caribbean Athletic Confederation]] (CACAC) LMA is invited to participate at the *[[CARIFTA Games]]
