'''''Switch''''' is a 2007 Norwegian snowboard film. The main actors are [[Sebastian Stigar]], [[Ida Elise Broch]], [[Peter Stormare]] and [[Hilde Lyrån]]. The film was nominated to an [[Amanda (award)|Amanda]] for the best youth film, but ended up at second place, beaten by ''[[Mannen som elsket Yngve]]'' (''The man who loved Yngve'').

