'''Tour of Libya''' is a professional [[road bicycle racing|road cycling]] [[stage race]] held annually each March in [[Libya]]. The circuit is 860&nbsp;km long.<ref>[http://za.country.csc.com/en/ne/pr/10006.shtml CSC South Africa: Willemse Jnr moves up in Tour of Libya 20 March 2007<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20070514210158/http://za.country.csc.com/en/ne/pr/10006.shtml |date=14 May 2007 }}</ref> Tour of Libya is part of the [[UCI Africa Tour]].

